{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "b1nntu-taimes-public-2026",
    "name": "Binntu Public API (full-info) - Taimes",
    "description": "Endpoints públicos de binntu-nest con `full-info` para consumo desde Taimes.\n\nTodos los endpoints son `GET` sin autenticación (usan `@OptionalAuth`).\n\n**Variables de colección:**\n- `baseUrl`: URL base del backend (default: `http://localhost:8080`)\n- `townId`: UUID del pueblo a filtrar (opcional)\n\n**Filtros comunes (query params):**\n- `search`: texto de búsqueda\n- `sort-by`: campo de ordenamiento\n- `town-id`: UUID del pueblo\n- `categories`: lista UUIDs separados por coma\n- `facilities`: lista UUIDs separados por coma\n- `ratings`: lista de números 1-5 separados por coma\n- `distance-ranges`: rangos de distancia (ej: `0-5,5-10`)\n- `price-ranges`: rangos de precio (ej: `0-50000,50000-100000`)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Restaurants - Full Info",
      "request": {
        "method": "GET",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Accept", "value": "application/json" }
        ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/restaurants/public/full-info?town-id={{townId}}",
          "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
          "path": ["api", "restaurants", "public", "full-info"],
          "query": [
            { "key": "town-id", "value": "{{townId}}", "description": "UUID del pueblo (opcional)" },
            { "key": "search", "value": "", "description": "Búsqueda por texto", "disabled": true },
            { "key": "sort-by", "value": "", "description": "Campo de ordenamiento", "disabled": true },
            { "key": "categories", "value": "", "description": "UUIDs separados por coma", "disabled": true },
            { "key": "facilities", "value": "", "description": "UUIDs separados por coma", "disabled": true },
            { "key": "ratings", "value": "", "description": "Ej: 4,5", "disabled": true },
            { "key": "distance-ranges", "value": "", "description": "Ej: 0-5,5-10", "disabled": true },
            { "key": "price-ranges", "value": "", "description": "Ej: 0-50000,50000-100000", "disabled": true }
          ]
        },
        "description": "Lista de restaurantes públicos con información completa (incluye categorías, facilidades, imágenes, ratings, etc.)."
      },
      "response": []
    },
